latestIgtvVideos.title: My weekly skin care routine 🌼🌸
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I’ve a  dry and very sensitive skin so I don’t prefer to go out for cleanups 
Instead I prefer my weekly clean up at home 💓
Using my 4 favourite products 💓 @aromamagicindia  mineral glow scrub - it scrubs away the dead skin gently giving it a natural glow 
It works best for me 💓  @aromamagicindia brightening beauty pack - it purify , soften and enhance the complexing 
It gives ab instant glow 💓charcoal mask 
You can use any charcoal mask 
I prefer to apply it only on my nose coz my skin is very sensitive 
It removes away the dead skin 
Last up I use kara face mask for hydration’s 💓
You can use any face mask 💓

Thanks for watching ❤️❤️
